{"tid":684832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國國台辦：「中國台北」選手奪金「全體中國人驕傲」    台聯駁斥：誰跟你中國人","createTime":"2018-05-31T02:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T11:46:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"90c401f4a84b9c6095a39eecc6ba8a43a201bcd5","tid":684832,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:02:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2442523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2442523&d=%2F5LYDKwjzmfGUvyXAHfK1DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=fb70823d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2442523&h=b1305a01\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2442523</a><br />\n<br />\n針對「2020東京奧運台灣正名公投」提案，中國國台辦今表示台灣選手以「中國台北」名義出賽並摘金奪銀，是「兩岸全體中國人的驕傲」，並稱此公投將自食惡果。對此，台灣團結聯盟反嗆「誰跟你兩岸中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n國台辦發言人安峰山今於記者會表示，多年來在「奧會模式」下，台灣體育健兒能參加包括奧運在內的國際體育賽事且摘金奪銀，是「兩岸全體中國人的驕傲」。安痛批「奧運正名公投」只是為滿足島內極少數極端「台獨」分子一己之私，最終只會自食惡果。<br />\n<br />\n對此，台聯政策部主任陳嘉霖駁斥國台辦「誰跟你兩岸中國人！」並強調正名公投就是為擺脫一中架構的「中國台北（Chinese Taipei）」，安峰山的說法恰好凸顯了推動該公投的理由，即為「台灣不是中國的一部分」。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉霖強調，台灣、中國是兩個截然不同的國家，但台灣選手30多年來卻必須背負「Chinese Taipei」的奇怪隊名出賽，被矮化為中國的一個地區，台灣民主化進程走到今日，體育代表隊正名是轉型正義與解殖運動的必然結果。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉霖直言，雖然隊名「Chinese Taipei」是在1981年洛桑協議（也被稱為「奧會模式」）所規定名稱，但任何國際協議簽訂後，都可經由談判再次修改、終止或退出，推動代表隊正名，完全不影響台灣選手的參賽權。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉霖解釋，一但公投通過，政府就須依公投結果展開正名推動工作，結局只會有兩種情況，一為正名成功，讓台灣選手以台灣之名出賽；二是正名不成功，繼續以「Chinese Taipei」出賽，但在過程中至少可向國際發聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4e564542d27a72c1ef8f2768524d053bbcdc6","tid":684832,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4de07c3b73855b5bb54883b14676c4a9eabcfe45","tid":684832,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"被強國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ddd2811a9967f3efa8ab4ce5261f1d0a05252d","tid":684832,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"推上PTT"},{"pid":"67fccbdf84529bd5b73c7856b610dfc898e8e8f8","tid":684832,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://bowenpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/1-48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbowenpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F1-48.jpg&h=30645545&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbefaccd36d202b13d2f91da30cae1b6a879138f","tid":684832,"uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老未<br />\n打杖啦<br />\n<br />\n台灣練兵都係防中共姐<br />\n<br />\n而加世界咁撚亂，打鳩中國啦台灣仲等乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb14a2888dfdbe6dd7a76a1a0f155b4ea7b784df","tid":684832,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"自豪呀，驕傲=臭串，以前小學(殖民地時代)唔俾用"},{"pid":"289a5677f579c099276b8eca42769e8e2961be55","tid":684832,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebc032caca6cfe13c948a3439a7f75e43b4e38a","tid":684832,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"呢頭中國人<br />\n下一刻就炸到你吋草不生 玉石俱焚"},{"pid":"c067ab5668b602df7483633425f0c7ae07dad79d","tid":684832,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbefaccd36d202b13d2f91da30cae1b6a879138f","tid":684832,"uid":59014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老未<br />\n打杖啦<br />\n<br />\n台灣練兵都係防中共姐<br />\n<br />\n而加世界咁撚亂，打鳩中國啦台灣仲等乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g